<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l1">Wir ~ die <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> des Rats etc
                                <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc / Als der erber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l2">vnd veſt Görg <expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü
                                <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / vnd
                            <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l3">vnd <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> volkmeyr
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen einen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l6">frid <add><ab facs="#facs_475_line_1576406901253_1496">cʒwıſchen </ab></add> vns vnd <expan>frıdrıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex></expan> beredt vnd gemachet
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l7">auf ſant Jacobs tag ſchirſt kümt / den tag vnd die
                        nacht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l8">v̈ber vnd v̈ber on geuerde
                            <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frıd wöllen wir alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l9"><expan>getrewl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit Jm vnd allen den ſeinen on alles
                                <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l10">vnd in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit einen tag
                        cʒü Herſpruck cʒeſüchen / als vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l11">dann <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Görg <expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>cʒewiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> tüt / Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l12"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> xpi / xıȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_475" id="237r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> des rats etc.,
                                <expan>bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc., als der erber und vest Görg
                                <expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex></expan> czü
                            <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeyr,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesellen, einen frid
                            <add>czwischen</add> uns und <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex></expan> beredt und gemachet
                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf sant Jacobs tag schirst</q>25.07.1412</note></app> kümt den tag
                        und die nacht über und über on geverde, <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        frid wöllen wir also <expan>getrewl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit im und allen den seinen on alles
                                <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        czeit einen tag czü Herspruck cze süchen, als uns dann
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Görg <expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>cze wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> tüt. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go.</expan> D<expan>at<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
